Subject: [PATCH] ZEN_INTERACTIVE

---
 init/Kconfig        | 26 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 kernel/sched/fair.c | 25 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 mm/huge_memory.c    |  4 ++++
